### Workspace-level ignores (Eclipse/STS) ###
.metadata/

### Build output (all modules) ###
**/target/
**/build/
**/out/
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

### Logs / runtime ###
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/*.pid
**/*.seed

### Maven wrapper binary ###
**/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar

### Local Spring config / secrets ###
**/src/main/resources/application-local.properties
**/src/main/resources/application-local.yml
**/src/main/resources/application-local.yaml
**/src/main/resources/application-secret.properties
**/src/main/resources/application-secret.yml
**/src/main/resources/application-secret.yaml

### Environment files ###
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

### IDE settings ###
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings/
**/.factorypath
**/.springBeans
**/.sts4-cache/
**/.idea/
**/*.iws
**/*.iml
**/*.ipr
**/.vscode/

